org.jgrapes.portal.events

Class AddPageResources.ScriptResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jgrapes.portal.events.AddPageResources.ScriptResource
  • Enclosing class:
    AddPageResources

    public static class AddPageResources.ScriptResource
extends Object

    Represents a script resource that is to be loaded or evaluated by the browser. Note that a single instance can either be used for a URI or inline JavaScript, not for both.

        public AddPageResources.ScriptResource setProvides(String[] provides)
